To be honest, I wasn't happy with the old fy_xbox, it was too basic. There was barely any layers to it, basic lighting, and was unappealing. So I re-did it.


To install, go to Steam\cstrike\-STEAM USERNAME-\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps, extract there and enjoy!
